author: Sports Illustrated
title: Emmitt Smith Presents National Player of Year Award to DJ Lagway - video Dailymotion
text: Emmitt Smith Presents National Player of Year Award to DJ Lagway 47 minutes ago NFL legend Emmitt Smith recently presented the Gatorade National Player of the Year award to Florida's DJ Lagway. The two joined Robin Lundberg to discuss the future of the Gators, the Cowboys' reunion with Jimmy Johnson, and to make predictions for the Super Bowl and the national championship.
